{"tid":2331331,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"點解笨die出左咁撚多隻數碼暴龍game,都仲未超越到ps1果隻數碼暴龍世界1","createTime":"2020-12-18T16:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T00:32:54.000Z","uid":31637,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"77f77b72bb0bd56f3284cff1f1b068583760ccc1","tid":2331331,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"遊戲視角係好似diablo果類既online第三身,府視45度角<br />\n<br />\n但屌打晒打後出既所有數碼暴龍game<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以出返個模式近乎一樣既續集？<br />\n<br />\nRemake都好呀屌"},{"pid":"93fa9049c8390ce2699a21c3e6464394373cd2c9","tid":2331331,"uid":81668,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"近排法國psp有隻叫數碼獸世界：復元 (Digimon World Redigitize)差唔多玩法"},{"pid":"9c50c675dcad63577c60312f90dd8aed70b4ce36","tid":2331331,"uid":251957,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"數碼1即使J到流膿見骨也要再J下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好J到停唔到手"},{"pid":"2400621ca7da1c9a21259d16d61c4ac08f609ede","tid":2331331,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c50c675dcad63577c60312f90dd8aed70b4ce36","tid":2331331,"uid":251957,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"數碼1即使J到流膿見骨也要再J下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好J到停唔到手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:00:38.000Z","msg":"細個唔識玩成日整左隻大便獸出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1677ac64276e63f927f182bcb778891762a11ea2","tid":2331331,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"就係因為佢地一直要跟住第一代既影子走所以限制左創意"},{"pid":"3e54be827ffb30c3d1a3f124875ee55e25684f95","tid":2331331,"uid":31637,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"93fa9049c8390ce2699a21c3e6464394373cd2c9","tid":2331331,"uid":81668,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"近排法國psp有隻叫數碼獸世界：復元 (Digimon World Redigitize)差唔多玩法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T00:57:49.000Z","msg":"玩過,爆左十世<br />\n唔同PS1果隻,爆完你係唔會想玩第2次<br />\n<br />\n畫面係提升左<br />\n但係好多方面都仲係廢撚過PS1果隻<br />\n1. 第三身視角, 就算畫面提升左都覺得D數碼獸既模組柒柒地,膠膠地,有D肉酸<br />\n2. 太多人類角色進入數碼世界, 太熱鬧, 唔夠孤苦伶仃<br />\n3. 招攬數碼獸入村既方式千篇一律, 唔似PS1果隻咁有各種唔同既小遊戲小任務<br />\n4. PS1果隻正到連扭卡機,卡鋪都有, 含收集元素, 爆左仲可以繼續玩, PSP果隻爆左只剩競技場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩PSP果隻既感覺似玩緊國產RPG GAME., 例如仙劍4~6果D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3daabfec55560f7145184ce6bece4d51082db9fc","tid":2331331,"uid":39177,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3e54be827ffb30c3d1a3f124875ee55e25684f95","tid":2331331,"uid":31637,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"93fa9049c8390ce2699a21c3e6464394373cd2c9","tid":2331331,"uid":81668,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"近排法國psp有隻叫數碼獸世界：復元 (Digimon World Redigitize)差唔多玩法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T00:57:49.000Z","msg":"玩過,爆左十世<br />\n唔同PS1果隻,爆完你係唔會想玩第2次<br />\n<br />\n畫面係提升左<br />\n但係好多方面都仲係廢撚過PS1果隻<br />\n1. 第三身視角, 就算畫面提升左都覺得D數碼獸既模組柒柒地,膠膠地,有D肉酸<br />\n2. 太多人類角色進入數碼世界, 太熱鬧, 唔夠孤苦伶仃<br />\n3. 招攬數碼獸入村既方式千篇一律, 唔似PS1果隻咁有各種唔同既小遊戲小任務<br />\n4. PS1果隻正到連扭卡機,卡鋪都有, 含收集元素, 爆左仲可以繼續玩, PSP果隻爆左只剩競技場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩PSP果隻既感覺似玩緊國產RPG GAME., 例如仙劍4~6果D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:34:16.000Z","msg":"其實佢放多幾十一百隻數碼暴龍入去幫人養,繁榮度加到300-500先滿,就算同一模式同一畫質都大把人煲隻game"},{"pid":"e26ed06c0c897a275265f03f12ba291b258fac49","tid":2331331,"uid":10454,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"偵探個隻好撚好玩喎"},{"pid":"d8fd10ef0854c3783dc82fa310512bbea7d7214a","tid":2331331,"uid":53901,"lik